## 🔧 Browser-Based Development Workflow

### Setup (One-Time)

1. **Install Tampermonkey extension** (Chrome/Firefox/Edge)
2. **Create New Script:**
   - Tampermonkey Dashboard → "+" button
   - Paste Unit A code (from CU-012)
   - Save
3. **Navigate to:** https://aistudio.google.com/
4. **Open F12 DevTools** (Console tab)

### Development Cycle

```
1. Edit script in Tampermonkey editor
2. Save (Ctrl+S)
3. Reload AI Studio page (F5)
4. Check console for errors
5. Test functionality manually
6. Repeat
```

### Quick Debug Tips

